      ('A 2 kg book rests on a table. List all forces and their third-law partners.', ['Book weight (Earth pulls book down) ‚ÜĒ book pulls Earth up', 'Normal force (table pushes book up) ‚ÜĒ book pushes table down', 'Two pairs, not four separate forces', 'Third-law pairs act on different objects']),
      ('A 5 kg block is pushed at constant velocity by 20 N. Find friction force.', ['Constant v ‚Üí a=0 ‚Üí F_net=0', 'Applied force = friction force: f=20 N', 'f_k=20 N', 'őľ_k=f/FN=20/50=0.4']),
      ('A 3 kg block on 40¬į frictionless incline. Find acceleration (g=10).', ['a=g sinőł=10 sin40¬į‚Čą6.43 m/s¬≤', 'FN=mg cos40¬į=3(10)(0.766)=23 N', 'Net force along incline=3(6.43)=19.3 N', 'Acceleration=6.43 m/s¬≤ down the slope']),
      ('Atwood: m‚āĀ=3 kg, m‚āā=7 kg. Find a and T (g=10).', ['a=(7‚ąí3)(10)/(7+3)=40/10=4 m/s¬≤', 'T=m‚āĀ(g+a)=3(10+4)=42 N', 'Check: 7(10‚ąí4)=42 ‚úď', 'T=42 N']),
      ('A 60 kg person in elevator feels normal force 480 N. Find elevator acceleration (g=10).', ['FN‚ąímg=ma: 480‚ąí600=60a', '‚ąí120=60a ‚Üí a=‚ąí2 m/s¬≤', 'Downward acceleration at 2 m/s¬≤', 'Decelerating if moving up or accelerating down']),
      ('A 4 kg block on őľ_s=0.5, őľ_k=0.3 surface is pushed with 22 N. Does it move? If so, find a (g=10).', ['Max static: őľ_s¬∑mg=0.5(40)=20 N', '22 N > 20 N ‚Üí block moves', 'f_k=0.3(40)=12 N; F_net=22‚ąí12=10 N', 'a=10/4=2.5 m/s¬≤']),
      ('A 10 kg object has two horizontal forces: 50 N east, 30 N west. Find acceleration and direction.', ['F_net=50‚ąí30=20 N east', 'a=20/10=2 m/s¬≤ east', 'Net force determines acceleration direction', 'Object accelerates east']),
      ('Two blocks (6 kg and 4 kg) are connected by a string on a frictionless surface. A 20 N force pulls the 6 kg block. Find tension.', ['System: a=20/10=2 m/s¬≤', 'Isolate 4 kg block: T=4(2)=8 N', 'Or isolate 6 kg: 20‚ąíT=6(2)=12 ‚Üí T=8 N', 'T=8 N']),
      ('A 5 kg block slides down a 30¬į ramp with őľ_k=0.2. Find acceleration (g=10).', ['FN=mg cos30¬į=5(10)(‚ąö3/2)‚Čą43.3 N', 'f_k=0.2(43.3)‚Čą8.66 N', 'F_net=mg sin30¬į‚ąíf_k=25‚ąí8.66‚Čą16.34 N', 'a=16.34/5‚Čą3.27 m/s¬≤']),
